                        <ln>Eagon</ln>
                        <fn>William</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>William Eagon, formerly of Staunton, died in Canton, MO, of inflammation of
                    the liver. He was 56 years old.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
